        "content": "# \ud83c\udfe5 Healthcare NOC \u2014 Network & Device Operations Center\n\n**Real-time Infrastructure Monitoring** | Hospital-wide device status, alerts, and network health\n\nUse the template variables above to drill down by **Floor \u2192 Wing \u2192 Department \u2192 Device Type \u2192 Manufacturer** \u2022 All navigation is live-driven from metric tags",
